      <div class="about">
    
        <p>
            At CodeLeap, we believe every great tech career deserves a strong start. 
            Our platform is built specifically for software development bootcamp graduates
            who are ready to step into the tech industry but may not have previous professional experience.
            <br>
            We are here to bridge the gap between fresh talent and forward-thinking employers who value passion,
            creativity, and potential.<br>
            <br>
            Unlike traditional job boards, CodeLeap is laser-focused on entry-level opportunities that help
            new developers grow their skills, build their portfolios, and gain real-world experience.
            From project-based roles to junior developer positions, we curate roles that truly match,
            where our users are in their journey.<br>
            <br>

            We are more than a job platform, we are a stepping stone to your tech career.
        </p>
